T10TD4194E:135a-0: @135a ` // rje 'bangs dang bod btsun rnams la sbring yig bzhugs so//
T10TD4194E:135a-3: bod kyi spu rgyal mgo nag yongs kyi rje //
T10TD4194E:135a-4: khri srong lde'u btsan aag tshom mes kyi sras //
T10TD4194E:135a-5: rlung nam 'phrul gyi rgyal po'i dbon po yi //
T10TD4194E:135a-6: srong btsan sgam po spyan ras gzigs kyi sku //
T10TD4194E:135a-7: byang chub sems dpa'i sku rgyud gdud ma chad //
T10TD4194E:135a-8: 'gro drug nang na shes rig che ba'i mi //
T10TD4194E:135a-9: dug lnga sdong po rgyud drug kun gyi gzhi //
T10TD4194E:135a-10: khri rje thog btsan man chad brgyud ma yi //
T10TD4194E:135a-11: dge bcu thang khrims btsugs nas dul bar mdzad //
T10TD4194E:135a-12: rigs kyi sprul pa khri srong lde'u btsan gyis //
T10TD4194E:135a-13: 'gro ba'i mun pa'i skar khung dbye slad du //
T10TD4194E:135a-14: rgya gar yul gyi rdo rje gdan stengs su //
T10TD4194E:135a-15: sde snod gsum po sh'akya thub pa sa gsungs //
T10TD4194E:135a-16: kun dga' bo la sogs pa'i 'khor rnams smin //
T10TD4194E:135a-17: 'dzam bu'i gling gi snying po'i dbus su gyur //
T10TD4194E:135a-18: bsod nams che ba'i mkhas pa grangs kyis smin //
T10TD4194E:135a-19: de gsan thugs kyi rus pa bcas nas ni //
T10TD4194E:135a-20: bsod nams chung ba'i rgyal khams smin bya'i phyir //
T10TD4194E:135b-0: 'phags pa'i rigs can ma lus kun btsal @135b te ;
T10TD4194E:135b-1: bee ro tsa na ska ba dpal brtsegs dang //
T10TD4194E:135b-2: klu yi rgyal mtshan ye shes sde dang ni //
T10TD4194E:135b-3: ae ra aa ro manydzu la sogs la //
T10TD4194E:135b-4: nor gyi dam pa gser dngul dbyig bskur nas //
T10TD4194E:135b-5: rgya gar yul gyi dam chos len du brdzangs //
T10TD4194E:135b-6: bod kyi mun rum nag po'i skar khung phye /
T10TD4194E:135b-7: srid kyi chab srid mnga' thang dgung la reg / buddha gu hya bdag dngos glo ba dga' //
T10TD4194E:135b-8: chab srid yo ba kun gyi gzhung srong zhing //
T10TD4194E:135b-9: sprul pa'i rgyud ma chad pa'i nang na lde //
T10TD4194E:135b-10: khri srong lde'u btsan mnga' bdag zhal snga nas //
T10TD4194E:135b-11: mi chos lha chos mnga' thang rtse ru chibs //
T10TD4194E:135b-12: rin chen 'bar ba'i sku yi phung po la ;
T10TD4194E:135b-13: / rlung mkhris bad kan 'dus pa'i nad chen dang //
T10TD4194E:135b-14: stong phrag brgyad cu'i bgegs kyis ma btsal bar //
T10TD4194E:135b-15: 'jam dpal dang ni mu ri ta la khums /
T10TD4194E:135b-16: yas kyi sa nas bdag 'dra spyan 'dren pa //
T10TD4194E:135b-17: sku mnyel lags te bdag la dbang ma mchis //
T10TD4194E:135b-18: 'phags pa 'jam dpa' zhal nas bod yul du //
T10TD4194E:135b-19: khyod kyis phyin na srog dang 'bral bar gsungs //
T10TD4194E:135b-20: bdag la dbang med khri lan skyes lan du //
T10TD4194E:135b-21: man ngag yo ga aa ba ta ra brdzangs //
T10TD4194E:135b-22: bang chen mi gnyis po yi rtsed lan du //
T10TD4194E:135b-23: mngon par byang chub pa yi tan tra bshad //
T10TD4194E:135b-24: phyi nang gnyis kyi lag len mang po kun //
T10TD4194E:135b-25: gcig kyang ma lus dgos pa thams cad brdzangs //
T10TD4194E:135b-26: gzigs rtog mdzad la gzhan du shor ra re //
T10TD4194E:135b-27: bod kyi mi ni sgrin la tshor skyen te //
T10TD4194E:135b-28: mthod ba thams cad la'ur byed par 'gyur //
T10TD4194E:135b-29: nyes dmigs cha med dam chos stong bar byed //
T10TD4194E:135b-30: dmyal rgyu mang zhing 'bras bu brlag par 'chi'o //
T10TD4194E:135b-31: phyi nang gnyis kyi lag len sba bar mdzod //
T10TD4194E:135b-32: rtsed la skyes lan gnyis kyis 'gro don mdzod //
T10TD4194E:135b-33: khri srong lde'u btsan yas kyi yang dbon gyi //
T10TD4194E:135b-34: raksha gnyis kyi bu gnyis phyogs rigs gcod //
T10TD4194E:135b-35: bod kyi rgyal khams srid kyi mkhar bu yang //
T10TD4194E:135b-36: zhe dbon man chad srid mkhar zhig par mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:135b-37: zhabs 'degs nyung zhing dmangs mo chung mar len //
T10TD4194E:135b-38: mtha' yi kha bzhi kun du grong slong byed //
T10TD4194E:135b-39: rgyal po'i dbyar ni bus pa'i rtse 'jo 'bul //
T10TD4194E:135b-40: dmangs mo tshol zhing grong zan slong bar mchi //
T10TD4194E:136a-2: / btsan po 'jal yang rgyal khams mi bzhin du //
T10TD4194E:136a-3: ngo mtshar mi che zhes ni mi phyogs par //
T10TD4194E:136a-4: 'gron po ji bzhin rgyal nyal byed par mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136a-5: phyogs bzhir sgyur ba'i mkhas pas bsgyur ba'i chos //
T10TD4194E:136a-6: rgyal po smos shing yon tan brjod pa'i phyir //
T10TD4194E:136a-7: sde snod gsum po'i bka' rgyud ma lus pa //
T10TD4194E:136a-8: mda' bdag phyir smos dpon sras drin du mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136a-9: sku shugs phyung la bka' rgyud ma lus pa //
T10TD4194E:136a-10: lnga bcu rtsa dgu'i bar du bsgyur ba mdzod //
T10TD4194E:136a-11: drug cu na ni 'jig rten 'das nas ni //
T10TD4194E:136a-12: rgyal khams gzhan du skye ba bzhes par mchi'o ;
T10TD4194E:136a-13: /'gro ba ris drug mtho dman gar skye pa //
T10TD4194E:136a-14: rang byung rig pa'i rgyal po rang dbang che //
T10TD4194E:136a-15: rdzas kyi shes pa shes pa'i nang na dbul //
T10TD4194E:136a-16: sems kyi mtshan nyid shes pa phyug ces mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136a-17: de phyir sems kyi mtshan nyid legs par rtogs //
T10TD4194E:136a-18: sems ni khang spre'u glog ste ris drug rgyu ;
T10TD4194E:136a-19: / mtho dman gar 'gro rang sems nyid dbang che //
T10TD4194E:136a-20: le lo ma mdzad rang sems ltas zhes mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136a-21: gros kyi gdams ngag man ngag bstan pa ni //
T10TD4194E:136a-22: rgyal po nyung na brin phyir khab gzhis skyungs //
T10TD4194E:136a-23: btsun mo gcig la dang du bzhes pa ni //
T10TD4194E:136a-24: 'phra mig g-yus spras brgyan cing mdzes pa dang /
T10TD4194E:136a-25: gcig sems gcig la chags shing sha tsha mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136a-26: srin bu gdong dmar bod kyi rgyal khams mi //
T10TD4194E:136a-27: dam tshig nyams shing mna' la mi 'dzem la //
T10TD4194E:136a-28: shes pa rags shing khong brnags chud ba yis //
T10TD4194E:136a-29: sngar byas khyad du gsod par 'os zhes mchi'o ;
T10TD4194E:136a-30: / bsod nams che bar dpag bsam shing bu 'khrungs //
T10TD4194E:136a-31: bsod nams chung ba'i bod kyi rgyal khams su //
T10TD4194E:136a-32: shing bu ta la phyis mi skye ba 'khrungs //
T10TD4194E:136a-33: shing la gnod kyis 'chad pa shol cig mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136a-34: gtsug lag khang dang mchod rten khang bzangs rnams //
T10TD4194E:136a-35: sdig pa kun la gnod de las rmang yin //
T10TD4194E:136a-36: dam chos bsgyur ba zhu thug dag tu mdzod //
T10TD4194E:136a-37: lan cig dus su tshad mar byed par mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136a-38: rgyal po'i rang bzhin gzhan dang smra mi bya //
T10TD4194E:136a-39: zugs thub gzobs la rab tu brtan par mdzod //
T10TD4194E:136b-0: thugs chen nang blon dpa' ba'i mi rnams @136b la ;
T10TD4194E:136b-1: / dgos don gces spras lhug par smos shes mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136b-2: srid la gnod pa'i gros ni me snyan bor //
T10TD4194E:136b-3: khengs par mi bya zhi dul bskyar zhing smra //
T10TD4194E:136b-4: gtsigs dang bya dga' blon po rnams la ni //
T10TD4194E:136b-5: ha cang ma che ran tsam bya zhes mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136b-6: blon po'i 'dod pa chu bzhin mi bzad pas //
T10TD4194E:136b-7: srid kyi mkhar ni 'jig pa'i nyes mchis te /
T10TD4194E:136b-8: srid kyis gal la bab pa'i dus na ni //
T10TD4194E:136b-9: sras la mi phangs sdig la mi 'dzem mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136b-10: bsgyur ba mi bla snyan khung bskyed pa dang //
T10TD4194E:136b-11: phyed tsam khyad du khums la rna la bzod //
T10TD4194E:136b-12: srid kyi chu mtha' rtog cing zad mi shes ;
T10TD4194E:136b-13: / dkon mchog gsum ni spyan ltar mdzod ces mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136b-14: theg pa kun la 'jug sgo re re ste //
T10TD4194E:136b-15: kun gyi sgo nas 'bras bu thob mod kyi //
T10TD4194E:136b-16: gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa dang du bzhes //
T10TD4194E:136b-17: bkri ba'i don du kun la'ang sbyad tshul bstan //
T10TD4194E:136b-18: rdo rje theg pa dang du bzhes mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136b-19: mtha' lho ba la rigs shes pa yod pa la //
T10TD4194E:136b-20: yid ches ma mdzad bong so bzhugs gnas rnams //
T10TD4194E:136b-21: kun du ma spong phung ba'i nyen mchis te //
T10TD4194E:136b-22: cal col ma mdzad co ge bzhugs zhes mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136b-23: btsun mo rnams dang bud med gzhan dag la //
T10TD4194E:136b-24: 'dod chags rang bzhin phyi phyir 'dod pa'i phyir //
T10TD4194E:136b-25: thugs kyis khug la ha cang sbyad mi bya //
T10TD4194E:136b-26: nga khyod sre zhing mtho dman med par mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136b-27: yid ches med par dgos don bsgrub mi bya //
T10TD4194E:136b-28: zas kyi sbyor shom zhim pos dgos mi bsten //
T10TD4194E:136b-29: zhe sas phyogs pa'i 'bangs la nye ring med //
T10TD4194E:136b-30: gzhan gyis mthong bar ma yin grong gzhan du ;
T10TD4194E:136b-31: / gnyen pos bdag kyang 'gro bar mi mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:136b-32: rgyal po'i rang bzhin rgya mtsho'i chu lta bu //
T10TD4194E:136b-33: zha lag phyogs bzhir rgyas nas slar yang 'du //
T10TD4194E:136b-34: rgyal po'i rang bzhin de bzhin yongs kyis bsgrub //
T10TD4194E:136b-35: rgya mtshos kun sangs chos kyis 'gro drug spongs //
T10TD4194E:136b-36: zha lag phyogs bzhir don byed sku gdung rnyed //
T10TD4194E:136b-37: so so snang yang slar la 'dus bzhin du //
T10TD4194E:136b-38: rlan gyis myu gu skyed bzhin gros rgya bskyed //
T10TD4194E:136b-39: chu yis 'bras bu bsgrub ltar dam chos bsgrub //
T10TD4194E:136b-40: rgya mtsho ma g-yos bzhin du g-yo mi bya //
T10TD4194E:136b-41: chu ni mnyen pa bzhin du khong mnyen bya //
T10TD4194E:137a-2: chu chen bzlog thabs med bzhin srid la bya //
T10TD4194E:137a-3: rgya mtsho kun la khyab bzhin dang lag bskyed //
T10TD4194E:137a-4: chu 'thung ngoms pa bzhin du gzhan ngoms bya //
T10TD4194E:137a-5: rgya mtshos chu rnams sdud bzhin 'khor rnams bsdu //
T10TD4194E:137a-6: chur ni gzugs brnyen gsal bzhin gsal bar bya //
T10TD4194E:137a-7: rgya mtsho yon tan ji ltar ldan pa bzhin //
T10TD4194E:137a-8: rgyal po gcig gi sku la ldan gyur na //
T10TD4194E:137a-9: spu rgyal bod kyi rgyal po'i mnga' bdag rgyud //
T10TD4194E:137a-10: mgo nag yongs kyi rje ru bskos zhes mchi'o //
T10TD4194E:137a-11: 'ol byung gdams ngag spyan sngar brdzangs pa 'di //
T10TD4194E:137a-12: mnga' bdag rgyal po'i mun pa'i skar khung mdzod //
T10TD4194E:137a-13: dus min rtag tu thugs la gdags par zhu /
T10TD4194E:137a-15: // / blon po rnams la brdzangs pa //
T10TD4194E:137a-16: khong dal smras pa btsan na blon pos rab tu chud //
T10TD4194E:137a-17: bud srid khye 'byin mi yi khong brna yis //
T10TD4194E:137a-18: so nams rgya yis chod na kun kyang drag par 'gyur //
T10TD4194E:137a-19: drang 'jam mig thag byed na srid mtha' yin //
T10TD4194E:137a-20: mkhas btsun sngags pa khyad du mi gsod bu tsha'i gter //
T10TD4194E:137a-21: khong gdug kha 'jam byed pa'i blon po 'jigs //
T10TD4194E:137a-22: 'o byams ban de 'khur ba'i blon po chos dang ldan //
T10TD4194E:137a-23: kun la snyoms par zas kyis bsten pa gzhan la byams //
T10TD4194E:137a-24: dul zhing gtang ba thub pa'i mi ni grogs por bcal //
T10TD4194E:137a-25: 'phral du khros pa lan mi ldon pa dgrar mi bya //
T10TD4194E:137a-26: dgra thabs zab mo dgra la byas pa rang la'o //
T10TD4194E:137a-27: nye dpung ma bshig gcig tu bsdus na dgra yang 'jigs //
T10TD4194E:137a-28: blo gtad mi la bu bzhin brtan par byed pa'i mi ni brling po yin //
T10TD4194E:137a-29: kha tshags dam la zas sgo yangs na yul mis rtsi //
T10TD4194E:137a-30: phur ma'i mi la spyi ched dang du blangs na smras pa nyan //
T10TD4194E:137a-31: yon tan can gyi mi la bkur sti byas na bsod nams che //
T10TD4194E:137a-32: shes rab can gyi mi la bslab sbyang byas na mkhas par 'gyur //
T10TD4194E:137a-33: dga' ba'i mi la gcam par phab nas smras na khong blo gtod //
T10TD4194E:137a-34: chung ma ji ltar mdzangs kyang gros blo gting mi gtad //
T10TD4194E:137a-35: skyes bu kun du grags pa tha shal che na nyams //
T10TD4194E:137a-36: ci la 'ang tshod zin sgrin khar mi 'dor rang lugs byed pa bzang //
T10TD4194E:137a-37: sngar byas 'gyod pa med par shes na mi yi blon po yin //
T10TD4194E:137b-0: dgra thabs mkhas la ral ka byed pa blon po @137b dpa' bo yin //
T10TD4194E:137b-1: kha 'jam che la khang ba rna chung ba'i mi la blo mi gtad //
T10TD4194E:137b-2: bskon thos rna gzod g-yos pa med na gdeng po che //
T10TD4194E:137b-3: pha ma dkon mchog phud du khur na rang gi ltar //
T10TD4194E:137b-4: ngan pa rnams la zhes sas phyogs na dman pa'i gzhi //
T10TD4194E:137b-5: dgra la sran du 'dzugs na phyis dgra 'jigs //
T10TD4194E:137b-6: khong ba rna chung ba'i mi la gnyer mi gtad //
T10TD4194E:137b-7: chung ma mdog sdug pho dad che ba blang mi bya //
T10TD4194E:137b-8: sge'u sres gud du byed ba'i chung ma gshin pa'i rtags //
T10TD4194E:137b-9: ngag 'jam khong yangs smra ba btsan de zhi na mdzangs //
T10TD4194E:137b-10: dpa' zhing phyogs che blo gtad thub pa pho zhes bya //
T10TD4194E:137b-11: tshig mkhas dgra la gnag na gnyen gyi rag 'jigs che //
T10TD4194E:137b-12: mi don byed pa rang don bzhin du 'bad na g-yo sgyu chung //
T10TD4194E:137b-13: rang don bzhag nas mi don byed pa do mi rtag / ngo dga' rma zhing kha rngam ngo mi rtag na khyo ga'i mo //
T10TD4194E:137b-14: 'jam la gros gal gcod zhi btsan na gros zla bya //
T10TD4194E:137b-15: dpa' la gnyid chung lag pa gtsang bas lam grogs bya //
T10TD4194E:137b-16: nye ring gang du 'gro yang grogs dang 'grogs //
T10TD4194E:137b-17: spro ring kha tshags dam pa'i 'khor re skyid //
T10TD4194E:137b-18: pha khu bzang po'i bu tsha ngan pa phos tshig che //
T10TD4194E:137b-19: 'phral du khong gyod nga ro che ba'i mi dang 'grogs pa byur //
T10TD4194E:137b-20: pha tshan bzang po'i gseb tu skyes pa'i ngan pa rang mthong che //
T10TD4194E:137b-21: kha dman khyim mtshes kun la sdang ba'i mi ni glang //
T10TD4194E:137b-22: mna' ma rnams dang 'khon par byed pa'i bshal thag yin //
T10TD4194E:137b-23: ngan las bu phos byas na gros re khug pa re //
T10TD4194E:137b-24: phar dan bu ru ngan na gros mjug 'thab mos byed //
T10TD4194E:137b-25: sngon du dpa' bo thod rgal byas na skyes bur 'gyur te dgra yang rtsi //
T10TD4194E:137b-26: mi btsan brdzun du smras pa'i tshig mi btsun //
T10TD4194E:137b-27: smra mi nyan pa'i nang du smra ba blun pa ma yin nam //
T10TD4194E:137b-28: rang shes chung ba yon tan can la smod pa ngan pa yin //
T10TD4194E:137b-29: pha mes yon tan smos shing rang spu ngan pa lo nyes yin //
T10TD4194E:137b-30: khong gyod gnyen la sdang ba bu lon ngan pa byol song yin //
T10TD4194E:137b-31: byas pa med par rang mthod che ba glen pa yin //
T10TD4194E:137b-32: bcol ba med pa'i las la 'jug pa smyon ba yin //
T10TD4194E:137b-33: zas ngor 'khrug ldan byed pa phung ba yin /
T10TD4194E:137b-35: // / sgom chen rnams la brdzangs pa //
T10TD4194E:137b-36: tshul chos mi bya shes pa'i sa mi gzung //
T10TD4194E:137b-37: sde snod gsum po kun la lta rtog bya //
T10TD4194E:138a-0: bltas pa'i tshig la mi brtag don la @138a * //
T10TD4194E:138a-2: lung la mkhas pa'i slob dpon rnams dang 'grogs //
T10TD4194E:138a-3: sgom chen yin zhes phug tu yong mi 'dug / yid ches med par bsgom par tshul mi bcos //
T10TD4194E:138a-4: the tshom bcad cing mkhas pa'i zhal yang lta //
T10TD4194E:138a-5: the tshom chod cing blo la snang ba dang //
T10TD4194E:138a-6: sgom pa'i gol sgrib chod cing don shes shing //
T10TD4194E:138a-7: rus sbal kho gor nang na 'dug pa de //
T10TD4194E:138a-8: brkyang bskum 'dug 'gro gzhan gyis ma mthong ltar //
T10TD4194E:138a-9: 'khor gyis slebs par ma yin dben par 'dug / snying po don las nyin mtshan 'byung mi bya //
T10TD4194E:138a-10: chung ma gshin yang bsgom g-yog bya ba min //
T10TD4194E:138a-11: 'du long ngan par 'khor du bsten mi rung //
T10TD4194E:138a-12: rang sems dpang du btsugs sa la yengs mi bya //
T10TD4194E:138a-13: g-yeng dang bying rmugs yod zhig yod gyur na //
T10TD4194E:138a-14: tshul 'chos mi bya bla ma rnams la dri //
T10TD4194E:138a-15: thams cad mnyam pa'i snying por gyur pa'i rtags //
T10TD4194E:138a-16: ci la'ang chags thogs mi mnga' mnyam par 'gyur ;
T10TD4194E:138a-17: / de 'dra'i sgom chen sangs rgyas rnams dang mtshungs //
T10TD4194E:138a-18: dus min rtag tu sems la gdams dag 'di //
T10TD4194E:138a-19: sgom chen rnams kyi sems la shar bar smon /
T10TD4194E:138a-21: // / spyi'i ban de rnams la brdzangs pa //
T10TD4194E:138a-22: mi dge bcu spangs dge ba bcu las ni //
T10TD4194E:138a-23: lus ngag yid gsum dus bzhir g-yo mi bya //
T10TD4194E:138a-24: dam chos zab mo'i phyir ni srog gis bor //
T10TD4194E:138a-25: mkhas su re zhes shes pa'i sa mi gzung //
T10TD4194E:138a-26: bdag gis shes kyang the tshom gzhan la dri //
T10TD4194E:138a-27: chos kyi srid pa sa gsum sems pa bzhin //
T10TD4194E:138a-28: doms par mi bya shes rab gsum gyis bslab /
T10TD4194E:138a-29: nges pa rang la med par gzhan mi bslab //
T10TD4194E:138a-30: bsrung ba rnam gsum zhing tshigs bzhin du bsrung //
T10TD4194E:138a-31: rdo rje slob dpon yi dam lha ltar bkur //
T10TD4194E:138a-32: man ngag zab mo mig gi 'bras ltar btsa' //
T10TD4194E:138a-33: theg pa kun la mkhas kyang gsang theg la //
T10TD4194E:138a-34: gzhan shes de la ma 'byor ban de ni //
T10TD4194E:138a-35: theg gzhan shes kyang gsang theg ma 'byor na //
T10TD4194E:138a-36: gser 'dod bong ba rnyed pa ji bzhin no //
T10TD4194E:138a-37: nyon mongs lnga po skye rgyud ma chod par //
T10TD4194E:138a-38: btsun par skye rgyud gcod pa snying re rje //
T10TD4194E:138a-39: nyon mongs ma spangs btsun ba gnyis mi 'phrugs //
T10TD4194E:138a-40: sa bon rul ba'i 'bras bu ji bzhin no //
T10TD4194E:138b-0: nyon mongs lnga po @138b dug sdod ma bsgyel bar //
T10TD4194E:138b-1: skur nas lha phyag 'tshal ba snying re rje /
T10TD4194E:138b-2: dug sngo dam bsgyel za bsrung gnyis mi 'phrugs //
T10TD4194E:138b-3: skyer tsher dar gyis phur pa ji bzhin no //
T10TD4194E:138b-4: nyon mongs lnga po dbyings su ma bskor bar //
T10TD4194E:138b-5: mchod rten bskor ba byed par snying re rje //
T10TD4194E:138b-6: chos dbyings ma mthong bskor ba gnyis mi 'phrugs //
T10TD4194E:138b-7: mar 'dod lha khang khyis bskor ji bzhin no //
T10TD4194E:138b-8: nyon mongs lnga po rnam par ma dag par //
T10TD4194E:138b-9: gdong bkrus lag pa bsnyal ba snying re rje //
T10TD4194E:138b-10: rnam par ma dag 'khru ba gnyis mi 'phrugs //
T10TD4194E:138b-11: bre ka nas kyis bcad pa ji bzhin no //
T10TD4194E:138b-12: nyon mongs lnga po zhi bar ma byas par ;
T10TD4194E:138b-13: / chos nyid zhi bar lta bar snying re rje //
T10TD4194E:138b-14: zhi bar ma byas lta ba gnyis mi 'phrugs //
T10TD4194E:138b-15: char ma gnam sdong ljong bu ji bzhin no //
T10TD4194E:138b-16: nyon mongs lnga po mgo bo ma bregs par //
T10TD4194E:138b-17: mgo zlum dpung zlum byed pa snying re rje //
T10TD4194E:138b-18: nyon mongs ma bregs mgo zlum gnyis mi 'phrugs //
T10TD4194E:138b-19: mun gnag nad na rdzas tshol ji bzhin no //
T10TD4194E:138b-20: nyon mongs lnga po dul bar ma byas par //
T10TD4194E:138b-21: pha rol dgra dpung 'joms pa snying re rje //
T10TD4194E:138b-22: dul bar ma byas dgra 'joms gnyis mi 'phrugs //
T10TD4194E:138b-23: ri gzar rbab shor 'dzin pa ji bzhin no //
T10TD4194E:138b-24: chos nyid zab mo lta bas klong du bya //
T10TD4194E:138b-25: spyod pas 'gro don bsam gtan rgyun mi bcad //
T10TD4194E:138b-26: ye shes ral gris skye rgyud gcad par rigs //
T10TD4194E:138b-27: nyon mongs lnga pos ldang ba gnas su bstim //
T10TD4194E:138b-28: yang ldang yang ldang byed na chos nyid bsam //
T10TD4194E:138b-29: mnyam pa'i don la bsam ba'i gtan la gzhug / rang dbang med par gzhan dbang bskur mi bya //
T10TD4194E:138b-30: dus gsum chos kyi mtshan nyid blo la gzhag / gsang sdags zab mo grong yul mi la ni //
T10TD4194E:138b-31: bstan par mi bya rnga dril yang mi brdung //
T10TD4194E:138b-32: yas ra yas lug mkhas zhes gsad mi bya //
T10TD4194E:138b-33: pho mo mang po'i nang du sgrub pa byed par khrel //
T10TD4194E:138b-34: zas nor gsang sngags zab mo yon du 'tshong ba smyos //
T10TD4194E:138b-35: gsang sngags bsam gtan yi dam nyid du nyo tshod byed pa med //
T10TD4194E:138b-36: ban de'i rang bzhin grong gi dbus mi 'dug / tshong la mi bza' sdig pa'i rmang gzhir 'gro //
T10TD4194E:138b-37: pho bla mi byang chub ma'i dad kyang skyungs //
T10TD4194E:138b-38: be'u mang po mi bsrel sdig pa'i rgyu //
T10TD4194E:139a-0: nyin mtshan med par 'gro don byed 'dod @139a * //
T10TD4194E:139a-2: / rang sems dag na 'dod pa'i don la sgrub //
T10TD4194E:139a-3: mi nag skye bo mang po'i 'gro don yang //
T10TD4194E:139a-4: tshod yod mi bya bsam gtan nyid du bya //
T10TD4194E:139a-5: 'di rnams ma nor shes pa ban de yin //
T10TD4194E:139a-6: nyin re bzlas pa mi gcad skyo dub kyang mi bya //
T10TD4194E:139a-7: rtse gcig dang du blangs la bya ba yin //
T10TD4194E:139a-8: mkhas pa'i rang bzhin don la mkhas pa yin //
T10TD4194E:139a-9: tshig la mkhas pa ne tsho tshig zlos mkhas //
T10TD4194E:139a-10: rtse gcig yang dag bden pa'i rlung las ni //
T10TD4194E:139a-11: rang sems dpang du btsugs la nyams mi bya //
T10TD4194E:139a-12: nyin mtshan med par chos kyi don la ni //
T10TD4194E:139a-13: dus gsum 'du 'bral med par ting 'dzin bya //
T10TD4194E:139a-14: shes pa tshe yang mkhas pa'i sa mi gzung //
T10TD4194E:139a-15: rdo rje slob dpon yi dam lha bzhin du //
T10TD4194E:139a-16: khur zhing rtse gcig yi dam nyid du bya //
T10TD4194E:139a-17: de dang mi 'brel brtse gdung tshe mar 'grogs //
T10TD4194E:139a-18: bden pa ston pa'i rdo rje slob dpon ni //
T10TD4194E:139a-19: mig gi 'bras ltar bkur ba'i rang bzhin la //
T10TD4194E:139a-20: g-yog 'khor ngan pa slob dpon spong byed pa //
T10TD4194E:139a-21: nyan byed mi de blun po spre'u zhes bya //
T10TD4194E:139a-22: 'di rnams bdag gis mdo tsam bstan pa 'di //
T10TD4194E:139a-23: bod kyi rgyal khams phan bde'i sems la ni //
T10TD4194E:139a-24: gdams ngag 'di ni kun la shar bar smon /
T10TD4194E:139a-26: // / slob dpon chen po sangs rgyas gsang bas bod kyi rgyal po khri srong lde'u btsan rje 'bangs dang /
T10TD4194E:139a-27: bod btsun rnams la brdzangs pa'i spring yig go//
